{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":6,"day":17}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"光辉指示照征途——纪念毛主席关于民兵工作“三落实”指示十五周年","authors":["晓江/高原/梁明江"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝书五卷到西沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西沙宝岛添壮美；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士、民兵勤学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心更红呵眼更锐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民联防守海疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜墙铁壁不可摧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓江摄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘阴永义乡民兵队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"模范作用人敬佩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产、战斗打先锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣称号色不褪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远坚持“三落实”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢记华政委的教诲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（永义乡“模范民兵中队”，是当年华国锋同志担任湘阴县县委书记兼县大队政委时亲自培养、树立的。）汪斌摄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葫芦队员胆气壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏平黄河千层浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两代民兵一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠狠揭批“四人帮”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东旗帜高高举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命传统大发扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙耀和摄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组织落实队伍强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政治落实有方向；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军事落实武艺精，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳武结合打胜仗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四人帮”破坏“三落实”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戳穿它的黑心肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高原摄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民协同显神威，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛歼敌人“铁乌龟”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民战争力量大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想来指挥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里江山万里营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人有来必无回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁明江摄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏修亡我心不死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔岸处处起狼烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人磨刀我磨刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民同守边防线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不忘虎狼在面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睡觉也要睁只眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵辉摄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练罢射击架起枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除草施肥歌声朗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产训练两不误，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广阔田野摆战场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫祖国作贡献，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习大寨当闯将。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛利摄（本版照片均为王静配诗）"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"name":"人民战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"指示"}]}]}